quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  105,1,"Koo, shiwalolakhwo shinga Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yakhola Abandu beyinzofu balia?"
  105,2,"Shiyakhola ebifwanga biabu biabiiya?"
  105,3,"Mana nabarumila amayoni emikanda nemikanda."
  105,4,"Mana nikabalasila amachina keliloba liomumulilo."
  105,5,"Mana nabakhola shinga obunyasi bunyanyilwe!"
